description:
Did you ever want to use your webOS phone as a scientific calculator? TouchCalc lets you do just that. Connect your handset to our powerful Pirna backend, and get results in blazing speed.

A legacy of experience:
Bada and Symbian users love Tamoggemon TouchCalc. In its lifetime, the product has computed literally millions of queries. Now, this awesome power is also available to your webOS handset. If a computation is required, it just connects itself to the cluster – in just a jiffy, the results are back on your screen!

Easy to use:
Even though TouchCalc offers an amazing array of features, it remains stunningly easy to use. A team of experienced user interface designers works day and night to ensure that TouchCalc is the simplest scientific calculator on the market – a powerful calculator doesn’t have to be complex…

TouchCalc can graph!
Should you ever feel like graphing a function, TouchCalc has you covered as well. Our high-resolution graphs look stunning on low-end and high-end handsets alike!

Download TouchCalc today for free...
